name: NickelBus, You're #1 Bus Stop!
overview: Our service searches thousands of bus schedules, routes, and station locations all over the U.S. so we can find the ride that’s right for you. Select your “Leaving From” and “Going To” points, click “Search,” and you’ll be amazed with the number of travel possibilities. We’re a tech company founded with a mission to bring more travel opportunity awareness to millions of people, and you can find an adventure idea with our Travel Blog at NickelBus.com/blog. Happy traveling, and we personally invite you to make your next bus a NickelBus.
